<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Eden Thak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Eden lui hi taihsan ding lam ahi,
 Nichengin malam I en ui;
 Buoina meipi kithiel ding dan ei puoi,
 Kapa sunni tum a baihlam ngei.

[V2]
 Eden thak ka hun ngai na zen e,
 Sunni tumin ginna'n ka hun en hi;
 Aw, ma a ka len-guolte chiehsa cheng chu,
 Nau bang nui siu sieuin ka mui.

[V3]
 2 Lungkham ka kah ni hin en vielleng chu,
 Buoina meipi khela lang khu;
 A hawih na e, lungdeihte tuollenna,
 Lal Immanuel gam nuom ahi.

[V4]
 3. Khawvel a hin mang lo ding a um puoi,
 Kapin lungdeih I tha zing ui;
 Eden thak tuol nuoma lenghaw vang chu,
 A kaplai nau bang a nui kit tau.

[V5]
 4. Ngai mah lengle na gam tun ma hin chu,
 Ka kahna ding khuo a sawt ie;
 Na guotsa gam thiengah ei pui in la,
 Kap lai hi puon bangin bang tang ka.</lyrics>
<author>C.Z. Huala</author>
<hymn_number>213</hymn_number>
</song>